Harmony Gold Mining Says June Quarter Metal Production to Rise by About 3%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-15T12:01:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/harmony-gold-mining-says-june-quarter-metal-production-to-rise-by-about-3-.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. said gold
production for the June quarter is likely to be 3 percent higher
than the previous quarter, even after days lost because of
public holidays.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
